class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="artesa-winery" class="entry-website-title">Artesa Winery</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-3840x12791-20240613.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-3840x12791-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-3840x12791-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Artesa Winery"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.artesawinery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.artesawinery.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Napa, California, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Artesa Winery produces high-quality Pinot Noir and Chardonnay wines from its 150-acre vineyards in the Los Carneros region of Napa Valley. Thanks to its clean and professional look, the website effectively captures the winery's commitment to traditional winemaking techniques, emphasizing its sustainability ethos with an earthy color scheme and selection of visually engaging images.</p><p>The website's simple navigation options ensure users can easily peruse the company's history, shop its product range, and become a member of its wine club to receive additional savings and perks.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>Visitors are introduced to the winery's breathtaking views, outdoor areas, vineyards, and tasting room with an impactful hero video. The company's FAQ section is easily accessible and gives users a good overview of the company's wine-tasting experience.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE picked up a large number of contrast errors throughout the site, indicating that some body text could be displayed in a brighter color to ensure optimal readability. Google's PageSpeed Insights test reports slower-than-average page loading times on both desktop and mobile.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-3840x12791-20240613.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-3840x12791-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website performs well and gives visitors easy access to pertinent information, including the winery's contact options, tasting experiences, and seasonal events. The online shopping experience is intuitive, but the site's heavy graphics can slow down load times. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the website scored 93/100 in the performance category.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-824x12591-20240613.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-artesa-winery-824x12591-20240613.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>On mobile, the hero video plays without fault, and all images remain refined, contributing to a striking visual appeal that's accentuated by the effective use of a sandy color palette. Thanks to the site's ample page links and accessibility tools menu, visitors can easily find and read up on pertinent information. Unlike the desktop version, the website has an average performance score of 52/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="château-du-taillan" class="entry-website-title">Château du Taillan</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chateau-du-taillan-3840x15834-20240613.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chateau-du-taillan-3840x15834-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chateau-du-taillan-3840x15834-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
