class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="fallen-grape-wine-co" class="entry-website-title">Fallen Grape Wine Co.</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fallen-grape-wine-co-3840x15733-20240613.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fallen-grape-wine-co-3840x15733-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fallen-grape-wine-co-3840x15733-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Fallen Grape Wine Co."
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.fallengrape.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.fallengrape.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Santa Ynez, California, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Fallen Grape Wine Co. is a California-based winery that produces organically farmed, natural wines, particularly orange wine blends and red wines. The website's ethereal aesthetic and sustainability ethos appeal to environmentally-conscious consumers, while the use of soft color accents effectively reflects the company's love of natural beauty and refinement. Site navigation is relatively simple and the use of minimal images and graphics ensures a smooth performance, enhancing the overall user experience.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
